        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/l/b19c9b/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-12-17T23:10:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I buy this wine every year also, and find that it needs almost 10 years after vintage date to seem like it\u2019s coming into its own. I\u2019ve tried the '12 a couple of times and found it to be quite tight.</p>\n<p>Buying and aging this wine is an act of faith, but faith well placed.</p>",
